name: She Does It!
description: She Does It!  Yes, she does.  This dress made from recycled t shirts says Babes! on the back.  She can do anything when she wears this smart black and pink dress.  We have added crystals to the front.  The hem is accented with black knit that is woven and knotted about the dress.  The dress is sleeveless and can be worn over another T shirt for cooler weather.  It comes from a smoke free, pet free home.  OOAK dress available in Size 7.

name: Books T Shirt Dress
description: Books cover the skirt of this dress and the bodice, sleeves and ruffle coordinate perfectly with the book colors.  The back of the skirt is like the front.  This is a OOAK recycled T shirt dress and is available in Size 3.  If your little girl loves to read or go to the library, this is the perfect dress for the occasion.  It comes from a smoke free, pet free home.

name: Mash T Shirt Dress
description: The M*A*S*H recycled T used for the bodice is embroidered not printed.  I could not resist adding some camo from another T to create a military look.  What a great way to welcome Mom or Dad back from a deployment.  This is a OOAK dress and is available in Size 10.  It comes from a smoke free, pet free home.

name: Cabo T Shirt Dress
description: Recycled Cabo T shirt forms the bodice of this dress.  The blue skirt has an asymmetrical hemline for a unique fashion detail.  The dress is a OOAK creation and is available in Size 6.  It comes from a smoke free, pet free home.

name: Rainbow Tshirt Dress
description: Recycled T shirts were used to create this OOAK dress.  Knits that coordinate with the Tie Dye bodice give this a versatile look.  The hem has an added 4" red knit ruffle.  Available in Size 4.  It comes from a smoke free, pet free home.
